### Steps to Reproduce Issue
See above

The current `authorized_keys` already contains the key located in the `.pub` file and a few others (including comments):

```
xxxxxxxx@testing01:~$ cat .ssh/authorized_keys 
################################################################################
# This file is managed by the Salt, do not edit this file by hand!             #
# Instead, please contact xxxxxxxxxxxx@xxxxxxx.com if changes are required.    #
